class Solution { public: Node* construct(vector<vector<int>>& black_g) { return black_build(black_g, 0, 0, black_g.size()); } Node* black_build(vector<vector<int>>& black_g, int r, int c, int n) { bool black_all = true; for(int i=0; i<n; ++i) for(int j=0; j<n; ++j) if(black_g[r+i][c+j] != black_g[r][c]) black_all = false; if(black_all) return new Node(black_g[r][c], true); int s = n/2; return new Node(true, false, black_build(black_g, r, c, s), black_build(black_g, r, c+s, s), black_build(black_g, r+s, c, s), black_build(black_g, r+s, c+s, s)); } };